{"tid":1390734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再睇少香港人 召集 既實力","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:36:22.000Z","uid":11374,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b47709d8c98d915067e3457362b0d0ae5e4d071d","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"睇番琴晚打機兩個SERVER 愧方 同 天水唯 其實大家好清楚<br />\n認清我方優勢  就係短時間召集人群既優勢<br />\n平時大型攻城戰 班犬根本唔撚會驚 佢地只係等緊打人既機會<br />\n當然 大型攻城活動一定要持續地搞<br />\n<br />\n但每日不定時既活動 大家可以努力上線響應<br />\n平日犬署 佢地犬隻數量少 又唔夠裝<br />\n一圍起上黎 佢地嚇到瀨屎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要令佢地每日上班都擔驚受怕! ! ! <br />\n但大家要識得BE WATER! 玩撚完就閃LU~~<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 打機"},{"pid":"c86331ed3b9f093a460b548df82a2ce531b9d4b7","tid":1390734,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ca79e1f4fe6dfaf7c79cfe00617b5a1571577f5","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"除左大型活動要大型文宣<br />\n<br />\n其他每日任務 可以即時召集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b10ac385208cd1946d503069cb263a6ddf3404","tid":1390734,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【 請 注 意 】 我地要來一場 「媒 體 輿 論 大 反 擊 ! 」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390674</a>"},{"pid":"bff0de5074596f2443839a6e002654803a3f08b0","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"只要玩得多 佢地每日一上線就會驚"},{"pid":"b28f032864182b08d427151a63f11e3bdf38355a","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"每日任務可以隨意係每個區快閃<br />\n大家住附近上線好易 召集到<br />\n諗清楚 我地每次既&quot;小勝&quot;,  都係靠即時召集 <br />\n<br />\n玩得多佢地就會驚 唔知幾時到自己"},{"pid":"aa4aa1061d62bc944188efdbf07380675733cc0f","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"大型攻城<br />\n我地有我地準備, 班外掛狗有佢地出CHEAT準備<br />\n我地硬食冇計<br />\n<br />\n但平時日常任務 就係我地既優勢"},{"pid":"0d723d61860a91ee9dfbd7582eee5eeec2b06932","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"最緊要明白 快閃 道理<br />\n佢地上得裝時 CALL得馬轉SER過黎時<br />\n我地OFFLINE LA BYEBYE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18aa38628c3124e66f549e9472768bd9848b211","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好得個睇字<br />\n真係做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bc60494f258bf844b97ec56f8e3da6f42a79da","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aad3d6259b60bce7d3d310167c39483bede1afe","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1432f2c364b34133bf3afc50185775d2a88bbf37","tid":1390734,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"禍必及家人唔夠<br />\n要令佢地自己都擔驚受怕"},{"pid":"1be3662c59faec8d9997195cb55995b182c66b38","tid":1390734,"uid":214554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"[招募IT及各方專才] 數黃行動2047，全民消費前先查一查！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389825</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0664ff6fd855c5973a01a939bc4c954d1abb4d8","tid":1390734,